Title: 'The Adventures of Travelling '
DateModified: '2018-02-09'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/the-adventures-of-travelling
SetInCountry: Australia
Category: A decision that pushed me to the edge
AuthorName: Sandra Gomez
AuthorCountry: Australia
Text: "I travelled to Argentine and I connected with my heritage.  I saw everything\
  \ through the eyes of an adult this time round, as when I lived there as a child,\
  \ I took things for granted, however this time round, when I was there in Buenos\
  \ Aires Argentina, I felt I was somewhere in France sitting in a cafe eating a media\
  \ luna, only to realise I wasn\u2019t as the waiters and the people at the cafe\
  \ spoke Castellano!  And suddenly I smiled in delight! only to realise I was back,\
  \ where I was born."
